```

And add empty `.gitkeep` files to preserve the directory structure so people know where to put things when they clone the repo:
```
data/.gitkeep
data/raw/.gitkeep
data/intermediate/.gitkeep
data/intermediate/grid_samples/.gitkeep
data/misc/.gitkeep
results/.gitkeep
results/figures/.gitkeep
results/tables/.gitkeep